<section class="section_facts">
<div class="section__wrapper">
<h2>Donate and support our work today</h2>
<div class="facts--banner">
<div class="facts--info">
<div class="wrapper">
<h2><strong>Yemen Emergency</strong></h2>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Yemen is experiencing a humanitarian catastrophe.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Millions are struggling to survive and now face the threat of coronavirus.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>Please help us get life-saving aid on the ground before it's too late.&nbsp;</strong></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong><a class="btn yellow" href="https://donate.unhcr.org/gb/yemen/">DONATE NOW</a></strong></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="facts--figures">
<div class="wrapper">
<h2>£69</h2>
<p>could help displaced families access lifesaving medical care, clean water and safe shelter.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<hr />
<h2>£138</h2>
<p>could help provide a vulnerable family with an emergency coronavirus payment.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>
<hr />
<h2>£276</h2>
<p>could help&nbsp;two families pay for essentials such as&nbsp;food, rent and hygiene supplies.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="facts--image">
<a href="https://donate.unhcr.org/gb/yemen/" class="" data-src="/thumb1/5ef5b6e94.jpg">
<div class="image--bg" style="background-image: url('/thumb1/5ef5b6e94.jpg');">
<img src="/thumb1/5ef5b6e94.jpg" alt="Fullscreen button" />
</div>
</a>
</div>
